    <item>
      <title>油价小幅反弹，创五年来最长连跌纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，美国就业报告强于预期，且计划补充战略石油储备，油价反弹，但由于担心全球即将出现供应过剩，油价仍结束了自 2018 年底以来最长的单周下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 23:49:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市多头创下 2019 年以来最长单周涨幅：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/japanese-shares-eye-early-slump-after-yen-surge-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五公布的两项稳健的经济数据震动了市场，因市场猜测美国将能够摆脱经济衰退，股市收高。现在，这个故事的另一面是，债券交易员最终被迫削减对 2024 年降息的押注——发送收益率飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/japanese-shares-eye-early-slump-after-yen-surge-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 22:56:40 GMT</pubDate>
